1. Download Cosmology of Kyoto from The Collection Chamber and install it.
2. Extract contents of CosmologyOfKyoto_TCC to the game's root folder.
3. Download the latest DOSBox-X portable install from DOSBox-X github, and extract the contents of mingw-sdl2 in the DOSBox-X folder.
4. Click on LaunchCOK.bat to launch the game.
5. Enjoy !
